	"metadata": {
		"inclusion": "1. Connect the RGBW Controller to voltage supply\n2. Set the Z-Wave network main controller into learning mode\n3. Triple click the B-button or any switch connected to I1-I4 inputs",
		"exclusion": "1. Connect the RGBW Controller to voltage supply\n2. Set the Z-Wave network main controller into learning mode\n3. Triple click the B-button or any switch connected to I1-I4 inputs",
		"reset": "1. Disconnect voltage supply\n2. Press and hold the B-button located inside the RGBW Controller's casing\n3. Connect voltage supply still holding the B-button\n4. Release the B-button\n5. B channel will turn on (blue channel)\n6. Disconnect power supply",
